                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>from <persName>Mr Judah Turo</persName>. The assistance<lb/> we have rec'd places us\n                in good condition<lb/> I hope you fasted well. <persName>Mr De Silva</persName><lb/>\n                the Shomas of the <sic>Pourtugese</sic> Congregation<lb/> read almost all the\n                prayers during<lb/> the Holy days He is very clever<lb/> &amp; very valuable to that\n                congregation<lb/> In our synagogue <persName>Mr Gutheim</persName> had<lb/> his\n                usual arduous duties to perform<lb/> &amp; also Lectured <date>Kipoor</date> some\n                of<lb/> the prayers were read by <persName>Mr Kaufman</persName><lb/> the Chouchet\n                the congregation also<lb/> Increased his Salary all your<lb/> friends are well<lb/>\n                <persName>Mrs Hart</persName> &amp; family join<lb/> in kind regards with</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Yours Truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Hart</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>NB The Howard association<lb/> presented on Hebrew Benevolent<lb/> association with\n                $400.00</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3d795x35/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
